<!--
  Animica Explorer — Sparkle Appcast (stable channel)
  Serve this file over HTTPS at:
    https://updates.animica.dev/explorer/stable/appcast.xml

  IMPORTANT — Replace placeholder values:
    - enclosure@url (point to your notarized DMG/PKG)
    - enclosure@length (exact byte size)
    - enclosure@sparkle:edSignature (Ed25519 signature from Sparkle tooling)
